      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "2019 Honda Accord EX-L in mint condition. The engine and mechanical systems are in excellent working order with no issues. The interior shows no signs of wear and is in like-new condition throughout. The exterior paint and body are free of scratches, dents, or blemishes. All features and electronics function as intended.",
